data.description: On the 15th hole of Twin Lakes Country Club,you'll love the views off your huge back deck! This Twin Lakes townhouse has a tranquil setting and fenced in yard. It's light, bright, open and airy floor plan with a main floor primary suite and laundry. Soaring cathedral ceilings and skylights add appeal to this open concept floorplan featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a full unfinished basement. The kitchen will please the cook with lots of cabinet space and great work areas. the primary suite has a large closet and bath with soaking tub and separate shower. Enjoy an attached 2 car garage and ample storage options. It's move in ready with neutral carpet and paint. Just blocks from Lake Mary and a short walk to all Twin Lakes shops and restaurants not to mention golf out your backdoor.
